<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>晨报指挥台 · Design A</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #07111f;
      --bg-soft: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.76);
      --panel: rgba(9, 22, 39, 0.82);
      --panel-strong: rgba(12, 31, 54, 0.92);
      --border: rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.18);
      --text: #e7f1ff;
      --muted: #92a8c6;
      --accent: #63c7ff;
      --accent-2: #7d8bff;
      --success: #62f0b5;
      --warning: #ffd66b;
      --shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.16), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(125, 139, 255, 0.18), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #06101d 0%, #081522 48%, #040b14 100%);
      font-family: "PingFang SC", "SF Pro Display", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(130, 177, 255, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(130, 177, 255, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 48px 48px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42), transparent 78%);
    }
    .page {
      max-width: 1320px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 24px 56px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .deck {
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .panel {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13, 30, 52, 0.82), rgba(7, 18, 32, 0.9));
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }
    .panel::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), transparent 28%, transparent 76%, rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.06));
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 28px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    .hero-copy {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(98, 240, 181, 0.26);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--success);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: rgba(98, 240, 181, 0.09);
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 44px;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }
    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 760px;
    }
    .hero-meta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .meta-pill {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #dbe9ff;
      font-size: 13px;
      background: rgba(15, 36, 63, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.16);
    }
    .hero-side {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12, 33, 57, 0.92), rgba(8, 18, 31, 0.94));
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.16);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 18px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      align-content: start;
    }
    .hero-side-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    .hero-side-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .hero-side-item {
      display: grid;
      gap: 6px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.12);
    }
    .hero-side-item:last-child { border-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .hero-side-item strong { font-size: 18px; }
    .hero-side-item span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }
    .summary-panel, .details-panel {
      padding: 24px 24px 26px;
    }
    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .section-kicker {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .control-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .control-group {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12, 31, 54, 0.95), rgba(8, 18, 31, 0.95));
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.16);
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      align-content: start;
    }
    .control-group-title {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .control-group-copy {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .source-options,
    .time-options,
    .control-stack,
    .summary-meta-grid,
    .article-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .source-option,
    .time-option {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 11px 12px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(13, 30, 51, 0.82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.14);
      color: #dbe9ff;
    }
    .source-option input,
    .time-option input {
      margin-top: 2px;
      accent-color: var(--accent);
    }
    .source-option-text,
    .time-option-text {
      display: grid;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .source-option-title,
    .time-option-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #f0f7ff;
    }
    .source-option-note,
    .time-option-note,
    .field-note,
    .action-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }
    .field-block {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .field-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #dbe9ff;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .field-block select {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.18);
      background: rgba(9, 20, 34, 0.94);
      color: #dbe9ff;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .source-list {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin: 18px 0 22px;
    }
    .source-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.14);
      background: rgba(13, 30, 51, 0.82);
      color: #dbe9ff;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }
    .source-chip:hover {
      border-color: rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.34);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      background: rgba(16, 40, 68, 0.86);
    }
    .source-chip input {
      accent-color: var(--accent);
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .actions {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    button {
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #04111d;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #87efff);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.25);
    }
    .hint {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .error {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      color: #ffd8d8;
      background: rgba(157, 43, 43, 0.22);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 126, 126, 0.28);
    }
    .summary-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .summary-meta-card {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12, 31, 54, 0.95), rgba(8, 18, 31, 0.95));
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.16);
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .summary-meta-item {
      display: grid;
      gap: 5px;
    }
    .summary-meta-label {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .summary-meta-value {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .summary-link-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .summary-link-row a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.22);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .stat {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(14, 34, 58, 0.94), rgba(10, 22, 39, 0.92));
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.16);
    }
    .stat .label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .stat .value {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .stat .foot {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: rgba(231, 241, 255, 0.62);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .summary-side {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .brief-card {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12, 31, 54, 0.95), rgba(8, 18, 31, 0.95));
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.16);
    }
    .brief-label {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .brief-card p, .brief-card div {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .artifact-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .artifact-links a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.22);
    }
    .source-badges {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .source-badge {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(125, 139, 255, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(125, 139, 255, 0.22);
      color: #d8ddff;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .empty {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(10, 22, 39, 0.82);
      border: 1px dashed rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.14);
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .detail-toolbar {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .stage-compare-shell {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 18px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .stage-status-rail {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .stage-status-item,
    .stage-status-button {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
      display: grid;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.14);
      background: rgba(11, 26, 45, 0.96);
      color: #dbe9ff;
      box-shadow: none;
    }
    .stage-status-item {
      cursor: default;
    }
    .stage-status-button {
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .stage-status-button.is-active {
      border-color: rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.32);
      background: rgba(16, 40, 68, 0.92);
    }
    .stage-status-name {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #f0f7ff;
    }
    .stage-status-meta {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }
    .stage-compare-track {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .stage-compare-pair {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .stage-compare-panel {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11, 26, 45, 0.96), rgba(8, 17, 30, 0.98));
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.14);
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .stage-panel-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.12);
    }
    .stage-panel-count {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }
    .view-chip {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.18);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .stage-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .stage-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11, 26, 45, 0.96), rgba(8, 17, 30, 0.98));
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.14);
    }
    .stage-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .stage-head h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .stage-count {
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 199, 255, 0.18);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .article-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .article-item {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(16, 35, 59, 0.58);
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.12);
    }
    .article-item.is-removed {
      background: rgba(73, 34, 49, 0.42);
      border-style: dashed;
      border-color: rgba(230, 149, 166, 0.28);
    }
    .article-item a {
      color: #f0f7ff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .article-meta {
      margin-top: 7px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .article-summary {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: #c9d9ef;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      display: -webkit-box;
      -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
      -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .article-summary-toggle {
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.12);
      padding-top: 8px;
    }
    .article-summary-toggle summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .article-summary-toggle summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .article-summary-body {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: #c9d9ef;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .tag-list {
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .tag {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(98, 240, 181, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(98, 240, 181, 0.22);
      color: #9ff5cf;
      font-size: 11px;
    }
    .stage-details {
      margin-top: 8px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.12);
      padding-top: 10px;
    }
    .secondary-details {
      margin-top: 10px;
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.12);
      padding-top: 8px;
    }
    .stage-details summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      color: #dbe9ff;
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 8px 0 6px;
    }
    .stage-details summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .summary-meta {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .source-group-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .source-group-card {
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 12px;
      background: rgba(9, 20, 34, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(126, 179, 255, 0.1);
    }
    .source-group-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #dbe9ff;
    }
    .source-group-head strong {
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .source-group-head span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
    }
    .compact-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .compact-item {
      padding: 10px 11px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .hero,
      .summary-grid,
      .stage-grid,
      .control-layout,
      .stage-compare-shell,
      .stage-compare-pair { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="deck">
      <section class="panel hero">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">Morning Dispatch / Design A</div>
          <h1>晨报指挥台</h1>
          <p>面向晨间内容编排的深色新闻指挥舱预览稿。保留现有执行链路和数据结构，用更强的情报感、层次感和数据对比，把“选源、执行、判断、落稿”集中到一个高辨识度界面里。</p>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <span class="meta-pill">深色新闻指挥舱</span>
            <span class="meta-pill">本地预览专用</span>
            <span class="meta-pill">支持真实执行</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-side">
          <div class="hero-side-title">情报总览</div>
          <div class="hero-side-list">
            <div class="hero-side-item">
              <strong>信源控制</strong>
              <span>单页完成源选择、执行触发和异常提示</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-side-item">
              <strong>摘要判断</strong>
              <span>高对比统计区强化原始、过滤、入选的差异</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-side-item">
              <strong>阶段透视</strong>
              <span>四阶段文章明细按情报卡片组织，便于快速比对</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {% include "_preview_a_generation_options.html.j2" %}
      {% include "_preview_a_summary.html.j2" %}
      {% include "_preview_a_stage_details.html.j2" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
